<img class="alignnone wp-image-1240" src="http://wellnessway4u.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/images-2024-11-23T112119.593.jpeg" alt="Suchi Mudra ( Png Tree)" width="353" height="235" />
<h3><strong>How to Perform Suchi Mudra</strong></h3>
<ol>
 	<li>Sit comfortably in a cross-legged position or on a chair with your back straight.</li>
 	<li>Bring your hands to your lap and form a fist with your fingers.</li>
 	<li>Gradually extend your index finger while keeping the other fingers curled into your palm.</li>
 	<li>Maintain the gesture with both hands and place them on your knees or hold them in front of you.o</li>
 	<li>Breathe deeply and focus on releasing any negativity with each exhale.</li>
</ol>
